Desc: Crystals scattered around the byte world. Collect a specific amount of these crystals to contact the Escape Car's emergency channel.
Name: Byte Crystal

Desc: Escape car, warp car, all-powerful car... Whatever you call it, it still does the same thing.
Name: Escape Car

Desc: Touch it and you'll gain 1 HP. Don't waste time finding out how it works. Everything's possible in the world of bytes.
Name: Health Crystal

Desc: Pick it up and all monsters on the map will turn into edible food. Now take your revenge on the monsters!
Name: Foodie

Desc: Pick it up to move faster for a certain amount of time and turn all monsters on the map to running shoes. Touch the shoes to refresh the duration.
Name: Sprinter

Desc: The most common monster in the world of bytes. It doesn't have any skills. However, you will lose 1 HP if you touch it.
Name: Hybrid

Desc: A monster in the world of bytes. It moves fast in a straight line but doesn't look very flexible.
Name: Eclipser

Desc: A monster in the world of bytes. It can slow down things within a certain range around it. You will be automatically slowed down when you get close to it.
Name: Ooze

Desc: Running Shoes (1 = Duration (To Be Deleted), 2 = Speed Upon Consumption, 3 = Stack Speedup)
Name: Shoes

Desc: Pick it up to create a clone of yourself to attract the monsters. It will stun any monster it touches and eat Byte Crystals just like you.
Name: Clone

Desc: Pick it up and an escape route will automatically open up for you. "Watch this! Here's my escape route!"
Name: Portal
